room_title: Escape room "Swiss Original" by Adventure Rooms in Hartford
room_address: 282 Main Street Extension, Historic Sanseer Mill, Middletown, CT 06457
room_description:
Wonder how escape rooms came to be? Your team will take on the purest, most traditional form of room escapes. This bare-bones fashion of event spaces allows teams to fully immerse themselves in the puzzle solving, scavenger hunting, unlocking experience which gave birth to the escape room phenomena!
There are two identical rooms available at the location, each for 2-8 players.
